---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Case Studies - Donut Cove Consulting" 
  description="See how Donut Cove Consulting has helped businesses eliminate tedious tasks through process automation, custom applications, and system integrations."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center space-y-8">
        <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl md:text-6xl">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-tech-blue via-tech-purple to-tech-teal bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            Case Studies
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-tech-slate max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Real results from real businesses. See how we've helped teams eliminate tedious tasks and focus on meaningful work.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Case Studies -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-24">
      
      <!-- Case Study 1: Gracelyn Group -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-tech-blue-light rounded-full text-tech-blue-dark font-semibold text-sm">
            Professional Services
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-tech-charcoal">
            Gracelyn Group: Streamlined Incident Reporting
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-tech-slate leading-relaxed">
            Gracelyn Group's incident reporting process was slow and manual. Staff needed a faster system that didn't require learning new procedures or disrupting their established workflow.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-tech-blue rounded-full mt-2"></span>
              <span class="text-tech-slate font-medium">Automated data capture and processing</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-tech-blue rounded-full mt-2"></span>
              <span class="text-tech-slate font-medium">Maintained familiar workflow patterns</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-tech-blue rounded-full mt-2"></span>
              <span class="text-tech-slate font-medium">Seamless integration with existing systems</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-tech-blue-dark">80%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-tech-slate">Faster processing</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-tech-emerald-dark">Zero</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-tech-slate">Training required</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-tech-purple-dark">100%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-tech-slate">User adoption</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="lg:order-last">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-tech-blue-light to-tech-purple-light flex items-center justify-center p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-large border border-tech-border">
            <div class="text-center space-y-6">
              <div class="text-6xl">üìã</div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-tech-charcoal">
                Process Automation
              </div>
              <div class="text-tech-slate">
                Streamlined reporting workflow
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Case Study 2: CareRev -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="lg:order-1">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-tech-teal-light rounded-full text-tech-teal-dark font-semibold text-sm">
            Healthcare Technology
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-tech-charcoal mt-6">
            CareRev: Smart Fraud Detection
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-tech-slate leading-relaxed mt-6">
            CareRev's fraud team spent too much time reviewing false alerts and manually tracking suspicious patterns. They needed smarter tools to focus on real threats and investigate cases faster.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4 mt-8">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-tech-teal rounded-full mt-2"></span>
              <span class="text-tech-slate font-medium">Intelligent pattern recognition system</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
