              <span class="text-tech-slate font-medium">Streamlined auditor investigation tools</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-tech-teal rounded-full mt-2"></span>
              <span class="text-tech-slate font-medium">Eliminated hours of manual review</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-tech-teal-dark">20hrs</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-tech-slate">Saved weekly</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-tech-pink-dark">50%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-tech-slate">More efficient workflow</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-tech-purple-dark">80%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-tech-slate">Fewer false positives</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="lg:order-2">
          <div class="lg:order-1 bg-gradient-to-br from-tech-teal-light to-tech-emerald-light flex items-center justify-center p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-large border border-tech-border">
            <div class="text-center space-y-6">
              <div class="text-6xl">üîç</div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-tech-charcoal">
                Investigation Intelligence
              </div>
              <div class="text-tech-slate">
                Enhanced auditor workflows
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Case Study 3: Bug Reporting Integration -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-tech-emerald-light rounded-full text-tech-emerald-dark font-semibold text-sm">
            Software Development
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-tech-charcoal">
            Cross-Team Communication Bridge
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-tech-slate leading-relaxed">
            Customer support and development teams were losing critical bug information in handoffs. Issues took too long to resolve because important details got lost between systems and teams.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-tech-emerald rounded-full mt-2"></span>
              <span class="text-tech-slate font-medium">Seamless integration between siloed internal systems</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-tech-emerald rounded-full mt-2"></span>
              <span class="text-tech-slate font-medium">Preserved existing team workflows</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-tech-emerald rounded-full mt-2"></span>
              <span class="text-tech-slate font-medium">Real-time information sharing</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-tech-emerald-dark">1 Day</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-tech-slate">Faster resolution</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-tech-teal-dark">20%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-tech-slate">Team efficiency gain</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-tech-purple-dark">75+</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-tech-slate">Team members benefited</div>
            </div>
